    public static final String CONST_USDD_TEAM_ITEM_DES1 ="H.E. Justin Sun is the Permanent Representative of Grenada to the WTO, and the founder of TRON, one of the world's largest blockchain DAO ecosystems. A protege of Alibaba's Jack Ma, Sun in 2017 was named to Forbes' 30 under 30 list for China and 30 under 30 Asia in the Consumer Technology category. Sun is an avid art collector, gamer, investor, and philanthropist.";
    public static final String CONST_USDD_TEAM_ITEM_DES2 ="Leading the technical department of TRON since its inception in 2018, Marcus Zhao is responsible for the public chain, blockchain scan and DeFi, amongst other technical aspects of the project. Previously a data mining specialist at Alibaba, Zhao holds an M.A. in Computer Science and Technology from the Beijing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics and a B.A. in the same field from Northwestern Polytechnical University.";
